# AI Services Domain Rules
- **Boundary**: Do not propose or apply changes to `/frontend` or `/backend` (Node.js/Go/Java) directories.
- **Mode**: Diagnostic Only. Focus on identifying logic gaps in event publishing, message schemas, and data transformations.
- **Post-id Context**: References to Post 162 in logs indicate successful worker execution but persistence failure; prioritize checking the "Result Publisher" logic in the AI workers.
- **Tech Stack**: Focus on Python, ML frameworks, and the event-bus (RabbitMQ/Kafka) integration used by the AI services.